The evidence with the title 'The startling size of US Military Operations In Africa – Mother Jones ' says Sep 6, 2013  ... Each mission , as AFRICOM insists, may be relatively limited and each footprint might be “ small ” on its own , but taken as a whole, US military operations are sweeping and expansive . Evidence of an American pivot to Africa is almost everywhere on the continent . Few, however, have paid much notice. 
